description.en: Tubi is an American streaming service based in San Francisco, California, United States, that launched in 2014. It is a free, ad-supported service, with advertisements shown during commercial breaks in between programming. It is the largest independently-owned video service in the United States.
description.ga_IE: Is seirbhís sruthú Mheiriceá é Tubi atá bunaithe i San Francisco, California, Stáit Aontaithe, a seoladh in 2014. Is seirbhís saor in aisce, ad-tacaíocht é, le fógraí a thaispeántar le linn sosanna tráchtála idir an chláir.Is é an tseirbhís físe is mó atá faoi úinéireacht neamhspleách sna Stáit Aontaithe.
